Class AssignmentFilesAllPresent

java.lang.Object
assignmenttests.programlevel.AssignmentOperational
assignmenttests.programlevel.AssignmentFilesAllPresent
All Implemented Interfaces:
assignmenttests.AssignmentTest, assignmenttests.programlevel.ProgramTest
public class AssignmentFilesAllPresent extends assignmenttests.programlevel.AssignmentOperational
Class to verify that all required files are present in a student's assignment directory. If any expected files are missing, they will be stored in the `missingFiles` list.
